MANAGERIAL POSITIONS WITH THE COMPANY OR ONE OF ITS SUBSIDIARIES FOR AT LEAST FIVE YEARS, WITH THE EXCEPTION OF MR. CHESTNUTT, WHO HAS BEEN WITH THE COMPANY SINCE 2011, AND MR. SCOTTI, WHO HAS BEEN WITH THE COMPANY SINCE 2014. OFFICERS ARE

