ROY H. CHESTNUTT IS EXECUTIVE VICE PRESIDENT  STRATEGY, DEVELOPMENT AND PLANNING FOR VERIZON. FROM THE TIME HE JOINED THE COMPANY

IN 2011 UNTIL HE WAS APPOINTED TO HIS CURRENT ROLE IN JANUARY 2013, MR. CHESTNUTT WAS SENIOR VICE PRESIDENT OF CORPORATE STRATEGY. PRIOR TO JOINING VERIZON, MR. CHESTNUTT SERVED AS CORPORATE VICE PRESIDENT OF THE AMERICAS AT MOTOROLA

NETWORKS FROM JUNE 2010 TO JUNE 2011 AND AS CHAIRMAN AND CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER OF GRANDE COMMUNICATIONS NETWORKS (GRANDE), A FACILITIES-BASED PROVIDER OF BUNDLED COMMUNICATIONS SERVICES, FROM 2006 TO 2009. PRIOR TO JOINING GRANDE,

